The '''Cave of Elders''' was the only artificial structure in the [[ThonBoka]], a [[Nebula/Legends|nebula]] located within the remote [[Open Sea/Legends|Open Sea]] in the [[Centrality/Legends|Centrality]]. Believed to be the only structure ever constructed by the native [[Oswaft]] [[Species/Legends|species]], the Cave of Elders served as an important meeting place for the Oswaft. Constructed between the three small [[Star/Legends|stars]] at the center of the nebula, the Cave of Elders was a 20-[[Kilometer/Legends|kilometer]]<ref name="thonboka">''[[Lando Calrissian and the Starcave of ThonBoka]]''</ref> rotating sphere<ref name="gamer5">{{GamerCite|5|A Campaign Guide to the Centrality}}</ref> entirely made of precious gems, and was built to be an exacting replica of the ThonBoka as a whole.<ref name="thonboka" />

